MobileResponderRecallNoticeTaskAttachmentActionForm is an ActionForm
    action is MobileCreate
    use for smartphone
    title is "CommentsAndAttachments"
    Layout
        paragraph
            button of "<RecallNotice>_-_<RecallNotice.Name>"
                link is MobileRecallNoticeNav
                label is "Notice"
                display as link
        two column distributed
            column1
                Title
            column2
                visible when (HasAttachment)
                    Attachment.Title
                Attachment.File
                    label is "Attachment"
        paragraph
            Comment
